    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though there are no major rips. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some preventative maintenance and suspension work in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
